---
---
<section id="como-funciona" class="mt-32 sm:mt-56">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl sm:text-center">
      <h2 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-eco-green">Flujo del sistema</h2>
      <p class="mt-2 text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-pretty text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl sm:text-balance">Como funciona EcoRuta</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- 4-step flow with inline dt/dd -->
  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-7xl px-6 sm:mt-20 md:mt-24 lg:px-8">
    <dl class="mx-auto grid max-w-2xl grid-cols-1 gap-x-6 gap-y-10 text-base/7 text-gray-600 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none lg:grid-cols-4 lg:gap-x-8 lg:gap-y-16">
      <div class="relative pl-9">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <span class="absolute top-1 left-0 flex size-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-eco-green text-xs font-bold text-white">1</span>
          Captura.
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline"> Sensores IoT y reportes ciudadanos alimentan datos continuos de cada contenedor.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-9">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <span class="absolute top-1 left-0 flex size-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-eco-green text-xs font-bold text-white">2</span>
          Procesamiento.
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline"> IBM Watsonx y PostgreSQL con PostGIS procesan y almacenan datos geoespaciales en la nube.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-9">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <span class="absolute top-1 left-0 flex size-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-eco-green text-xs font-bold text-white">3</span>
          Optimizacion.
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline"> El motor de IA calcula rutas optimas y predice llenado futuro con machine learning.</dd>
      </div>
      <div class="relative pl-9">
        <dt class="inline font-semibold text-gray-900">
          <span class="absolute top-1 left-0 flex size-6 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-eco-green text-xs font-bold text-white">4</span>
          Accion.
        </dt>
        <dd class="inline"> Conductores reciben instrucciones claras. Gestores ven metricas. Ciudadanos reciben alertas.</dd>
      </div>
    </dl>
  </div>

  <!-- Two parallel flows -->
  <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-5xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Citizen -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-900/10">
        <h3 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-5 flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-blue-50">
            <svg class="size-5 text-blue-600" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M15.75 6a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0zM4.501 20.118a7.5 7.5 0 0114.998 0A17.933 17.933 0 0112 21.75c-2.676 0-5.216-.584-7.499-1.632z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Para el ciudadano
        </h3>
        <ol class="space-y-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-xs font-bold text-blue-600">1</span>Descarga la app (PWA, sin app store)</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-xs font-bold text-blue-600">2</span>Reporta contenedores desbordados o anomalias desde su celular</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-blue-50 text-xs font-bold text-blue-600">3</span>Recibe notificaciones sobre el servicio en su colonia</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <!-- Municipality -->
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 sm:p-8 ring-1 ring-gray-900/10">
        <h3 class="text-base/7 font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-5 flex items-center gap-2">
          <div class="flex size-8 items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-green-50">
            <svg class="size-5 text-eco-green" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M2.25 21h19.5m-18-18v18m10.5-18v18m6-13.5V21M6.75 6.75h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75m3-6h.75m-.75 3h.75m-.75 3h.75M6.75 21v-3.375c0-.621.504-1.125 1.125-1.125h2.25c.621 0 1.125.504 1.125 1.125V21M3 3h12m-.75 4.5H21m-3.75 0h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008zm0 3h.008v.008h-.008v-.008z"/></svg>
          </div>
          Para el municipio
        </h3>
        <ol class="space-y-4 text-sm/6 text-gray-600">
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-50 text-xs font-bold text-eco-green">1</span>Los sensores detectan contenedores criticos automaticamente</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-50 text-xs font-bold text-eco-green">2</span>El sistema genera rutas optimizadas y las asigna a conductores</li>
          <li class="flex gap-x-3"><span class="flex size-6 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-green-50 text-xs font-bold text-eco-green">3</span>Al final del turno, se genera un reporte de eficiencia automatico</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
